The paper focuses on the design of effective color ramps for visualizations, which is a topic that falls under the Human-Computer Interaction (cs.HC) and Graphics (cs.GR) sub-categories. The paper also uses algorithmic approaches to model designer practices, which could fall under the Computer Vision (cs.CV), Natural Language Processing (cs.CL), or Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories.
